<plot>BROKEN is the bittersweet love story between a father and daughter, and the unassuming drifter who becomes a vital part of their lives. Patty is a woman who has spent most of her adult life caring for her absentee father, now an invalid. Pike is a drifter who shows up one day looking for a way to make life right again. This story is about the friendship they develop, and how that friendship changes both their lives forever.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?083814</url></doc>
